OL,5, A new theatre production will leave its
OL,6, cast, crew and creative team behind    
OL,7, when it leaves London to tour the UK.  
OL,9,FIt's A Sin star Lydia West will appear 
OL,10,Fin the one-woman play about climate    
OL,11,Fchange at London's Barbican this week. 
OL,13,FThe show is powered by 10 cyclists on  
OL,14,Fstage, who pedal constantly to generate
OL,15,Fthe energy to cover the performance.   
OL,17,FBut when its London residency ends,    
OL,18,FWest and the team will not take the    
OL,19,Fshow to its other stops. Instead, local
OL,20,Fcrews will reassemble it in each area. 
